tributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVladimir%20Putin%20is%20starting%20to%20express%20his%20anger%20toward%20NATO%20nations%20Latvia%2C%20Estonia%2C%20and%20Lithuania.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20rhetoric%20sounds%20an%20awful%20lot%20like%20his%20statements%20before%20Russia%20attacked%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERussia's%20emerging%20narrative%20toward%20the%20Baltics%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfuture%20escalations%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-january-16-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ISW%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20leader%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20been%20intensifying%20his%20rhetoric%20against%20the%20Baltic%20states%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20potential%20%26quot%3Bfuture%20escalations%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20eastern%20NATO%20members%2C%20the%20Institute%20for%20Study%20of%20War%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-january-16-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20claimed%20that%20Latvia%20and%20other%20Baltic%20nations%20were%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20throwing%20out%26quot%3B%20ethnic%20Russian%20people%20from%20their%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20complaint%20refers%20to%20changes%20in%20Latvia's%20immigration%20law%20that%20require%20Russians%20living%20as%20permanent%20residents%20in%20the%20country%20to%20pass%20a%20Latvian%20language%20test%20if%20they%20want%20to%20stay%20there.%20Around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feng.lsm.lv%2Farticle%2Fsociety%2Fsociety%2F27.12.2023-over-1200-russians-might-have-to-be-expelled-from-latvia.a536843%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C200%20Russians%20were%20identified%20for%20deportation%3