0he%20wrote%20in%20his%20memoir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20funny%20that%20someone%20like%20Rental%20Person%20should%20be%20in%20demand.%20I%20suppose%20you%20could%20say%20my%20lack%20of%20individuality%20has%20become%20my%20'product%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20eccentric%20calling%20has%20earned%20him%20criticism.%20He%20says%20people%20have%20called%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20new-age%20gigolo%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Ba%20new-age%20beggar.%26quot%3B%20But%20Morimoto%20doesn't%20feel%20offended%20by%20those%20labels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20being%20a%20gigolo%20or%20beggar%20are%20potential%20ways%20of%20relating%20to%20people%2C%20and%20the%20word%20'new'%20sounds%20good%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20quite%20positive%20about%20these%20comments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20memoir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorimoto%20used%20to%20charge%2010%2C000%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20or%20%2468%2C%20per%20booking%2C%20per%20a%20September%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flifestyle%2Foddly-enough%2Fdream-job-japanese-man-who-gets-paid-do-nothing-2022-09-06%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20he%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmorimotoshoji%2Fstatus%2F1698705759004205559%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20charges%20his%20clients%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20would%20just%20accept%20reimbursement%20for%20travel%20expenses%20and%20the%20food%20and%20drink%20consumed%20during%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20I'm%20living%20on%20savings.%20What%20I%20do%20isn't%20really%20a%20business.%20Maybe%20it's%20best%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20something%20I'm%20doing%20for%20fun%20(like%20a%20trip%20abroad%20I've%20saved%20up%20for)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapanese-man-hired-to-