3%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20'Asli%20Azaadi'%20Claim%20Over%20Ram%20Temple%20Undermines%20Freedom%20Struggle%3A%20CPI(M)'s%20Sitaram%20Yechury%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18140611%2FGEDRHL7WoAAhp2m.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20January%2017%2C%20warned%20against%20religious%20polarisation%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20foundation%20stone-laying%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Jyoti%20Basu%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Studies%20and%20Research%20(JBCSSR)%20building%20to%20mark%20the%2015th%20death%20anniversary%20of%20former%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Jyoti%20Basu%2C%20Yechury%20criticised%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20portraying%20the%20ceremony%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Easli%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eazaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20real%20freedom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20claims%20that%20real%20freedom%20will%20be%20achieved%20on%20January%2022.%20It%20undermines%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20sacrifices%20of%20our%20freedom%20fighters%2C%20and%20the%20collective%20commitment%20of%20our%20founders%20to%20a%20secular%2C%20democratic%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yechury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20Yechury%20became%20the%20first%20politician%20to%20turn%20down%20an%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20under-construction%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20including%20Congress%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20have%20similarly%20declined.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20announced%20that%20on%20January%2022%2C%20she%20would%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20famous%20Kali%20temple%20in%20Kalighat%20and%20lead%20an%20interfaith%20rally%20which%20would%20culminate%20in%20a%20gurdwara.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20labelled%20her%20decision%20as%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccompetitive%20communalism%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20both%20Yechury%20and%20state%20secretary%20Mohammed%20Salim%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20refrain%20from%20indulging%20in%20politics%20based%20on%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20political%20party%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20its%20campaign%20to%20safeguard%20communal%20harmony%2C%20but%20such%20initiatives%20should%20avoid%20fostering%20competitive%20communalism%20or%20causing%20political%20polarisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yechury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWest%20Bengal%20Left%20Front%20chairman%20Biman%20Basu%2C%20CPI(M)%20state%20secretary%20Salim%2C%20along%20with%20other%20state%20leaders%20participated%20in%20a%20seminar%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Challenge%20to%20Safeguard%20Secular%20Democratic%20Republic.%E2%80%99%20The%20discussion%20emphasised%20the%20imperative%20of%20preserving%20the%20secular%2C%20socialist%2C%20and%20democratic%20principles%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20to%20combat%20the%20communal%20ideology%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705568319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18140611%2FGEDRHL7WoAAhp2m.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-asli-azaadi-claim-over-ram-temple-undermines-freedom-struggle-cpims-sitaram-yechury%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CPI(M)%20also%20labelled%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20decision%20on%20her%20activities%20on%20January%2022%20as%20a%20case%20of%20'competitive%20communalism.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-asli-azaadi-claim-over-ram-temple-undermines-freedom-struggle-cpims-sitaram-yechury%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EPFO%20Removes%20Aadhaar%20As%20Date%20Of%20Birth%20Proof%2C%20Check%20List%20Of%20Valid%20Documents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20decision%2C%20the%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20has%20removed%20the%20Aadhaar%20card%20from%20the%20list%20of%20documents%20acceptable%20as%20date%20of%20birth%20(DOB)%20proof.%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20EPFO%C2%A0notified%20the%20removal%20of%20Aadhaar%20Card%20as%20an%20acceptable%20document%20for%20date%20of%20Birth%20after%20a%20directive%20from%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI).%20In%20a%20circular%20issued%20on%20January%2016%2C%20EPFO%20noted%20that%20Aadhaar--%20which%20was%20being%20considered%20as%20proof%20of%20date%20of%20birth%20by%20several%20beneficiaries--%C2%A0is%20primarily%20an%20identity%20verification%20tool%20and%20not%20a%20proof%20of%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20has%20received%20approval%20from%20the%20Central%20Provident%20Fund%20Commissioner%20(CPFC).%20Some%20recent%20court%20judgments%20have%20also%20reinforced%20that%20Aadhaar%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20as%20proof%20of%20date%20of%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%20this%20connection%2C%20a%20letter%20has%20been%20received%20from%20UIDAI%20(copy%20attached)%2C%20wherein%20it%20has%20been%20stated%20that%20the%20use%20of%20an%20Aadhaar%2C%20as%20proof%20of%20DoB%20needs%20to%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20list%20of%20acceptable%20documents.%20Accordin