ot%3B%20He%20continued%20by%20explaining%20that%20while%20most%20people%20thought%20the%20clip%20was%20funny%2C%20however%2C%20certain%20people%20did%20not%20relate%20to%20it.%20%26quot%3BMost%20people%20took%20it%20as%20a%20joke%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20work%20at%20Amazon%2C%20you%20knew%20that%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20overexaggerating%20...%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20offended%20by%20my%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20offended%20by%20that%20video%2C%20I%20am%20sorry.%20I%20never%20meant%20to%20offend%20anyone%20or%20discriminate%20against%20anyone.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20funny%20video.%20I'm%20not%20just%20saying%20that.%20I%20already%20lost%20my%20job%20and%20am%20ineligible%20for%20rehire%2C%20so%20please%20forgive%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20in%20question%20was%20posted%20on%20December%206%20where%20he%20said%20that%20he%20worked%20an%20extra%20shift%20and%20was%20given%20the%20job%20of%20a%20picker%20at%20Amazon%20warehouse.%20%26quot%3BTell%20me%20why%20every%20other%20item%20I%20picked%20was%20either%20Fiji%20water%20or%20f******%20dog%20food%3F%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20needs%20to%20hear%20this%2C%20but%20stop%20buying%20water%20at%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20telling%20me%20you're%20out%20of%20water%2C%20you%20go%20on%20Amazon%2C%20and%20you%20wait%20two%20to%20three%20business%20days%20to%20get%20your%20f******%20water%2C%20bro%3F%20What%20are%20you%20drinking%20in%20the%20meantime%3F%20Take%20your%20lazy%20a-%20to%20the%20store%20and%20buy%20water%20there%20like%20normal%20people%20do.%20The%20next%20time%20I'm%20picking%20and%20I%20see%20some%20water%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20replace%20your%20Fiji%20water%20with%20Aquafina%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendall%20added%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20made%20jokes%20about%20what%20he%20would%20do%20to%20exact%20revenge%20on%20careless%