mething%20to%20be%20cherished''%2C%20but%20it%20is%20ultimately%20being%20''undermined%20by%20pornography.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20must%20defend%20love.%20Winning%20against%20the%20battle%20of%20lust%20can%20be%20a%20lifelong%20undertaking%2C''%20he%20said.%20The%20Pope%2C%20born%20in%20Argentina%2C%20warned%20that%20porn%20could%20give%20rise%20to%20addictive%20behaviours%2C%20and%20that%20lust%20leads%20to%20a%20''dangerous%20vice.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLust%20plunders%2C%20it%20robs%2C%20it%20consumes%20in%20haste%2C%20it%20does%20not%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20other%20but%20only%20to%20its%20own%20need%20and%20pleasure%3B%20lust%20judges%20every%20courtship%20a%20bore%2C%20it%20does%20not%20seek%20that%20synthesis%20between%20reason%2C%20drive%20and%20feeling%20that%20would%20help%20us%20to%20conduct%20existence%20wisely%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20pope%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fpope-sexual-pleasure-gift-from-god-lust-vatican%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Roman%20Catholic%20Church%20has%20spoken%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20porn.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20he%20called%20soft%20porn%20a%20temptation%20that%20%26quot%3Bweakens%20the%20priestly%20heart%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpornography-temptation-weakens-priestly-heart-pope-francis-warns-priests-3466169%5C%22%3Eaware%20of%20priests%20and%20nuns%20who%20watched%20porn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20advised%20them%20to%20remove%20temptation%20by%20eliminating%20it%20from%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20of%20you%20thinks%20if%20you've%20had%20the%20experience%20or%20had%20the%20temptation%20of%20digital%20pornography.%20It's%20a%20vice%20that%20so%20many%20people%20have%2C%20so%20many%20laymen%2C%20so%20many%20lay%20women%2C%20and%20even%20priests%20and%20nuns%2C%26quot%3B%20Pope%20Francis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20criminal%20pornography%20like%20child%20abuse%2C%20where%20you%20see%20live%20cases%20of%20abuse%3A%20that's%20already%20degeneracy.%20But%20of%20the%20more%20'normal'%20pornography%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20Pope%20Francis--one%20of%20the%20most%20progressive%20leaders%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Church--has%20been%20quite%20frank%20while%20discussing%20topics%20of%20sexuality.%20Last%20year%2C%C2%A0he%20formally%20approved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvatican-pope-francis-blessings-for-same-sex-couples-approved-by-the-vatican-in-landmark-ruling-4698013%5C%22%3Eallowing%20priests%20to%20bless%20same-sex%20couples%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20not%20part%20of%20regular%20Church%20rituals%20or%20liturgies.%C2%A0He%20responded%20to%20the%20criticism%20from%20some%20priests%20who%20refused%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20suggesting%20that%20those%20in%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20who%20have%20resisted%20it%20have%20jumped%20to%20%26quot%3Bugly%20conclusions%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20do%20not%20understand%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%20he%20also%20praised%20the%20virtues%20of%20sex%20in%20a%20documentary%20released%20in%20April%202023%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20beautiful%20things%20that%20God%20has%20given%20to%20the%20human%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20express%20yourself%20sexually%20is%20a%20richness.%20So%20anything%20that%20detracts%20from%20real%20sexual%20expression%20lessens%20you%20and%20depletes%20this%20richness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20also%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20masturbation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705564980000%2C%22visual%22