port.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcwashington.com%2Finvestigations%2Fdulles-traveler-tells-how-she-found-her-stolen-laptop-and-helped-track-down-the-thief%2F3512514%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENBC4%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Jane%20said%20that%20even%20though%20the%20police%20identified%20the%20employee%2C%20he%20was%20not%20immediately%20arrested%20and%20was%20allowed%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20job%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%20while%20the%20investigation%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThey%20couldn't%20arrest%20him%20yet%20because%20they%20needed%20more%20in%20order%20to%20get%20a%20search%20warrant%20to%20get%20my%20computer%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20things%20changed%20when%20Ms%20Jane%20received%20a%20message%20one%20morning%20from%20an%20anonymous%20Instagram%20account%2C%20which%20contained%20a%20nude%20photo%20of%20herself.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20had%20no%20doubt%20where%20the%20photo%20came%20from.%20It%20was%20part%20of%20an%20art%20project%20stored%20on%20her%20laptop%20and%20said%20she%20hadn't%20sent%20it%20to%20anyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Jane%20immediately%20contacted%20the%20MWAA%20investigator%20working%20on%20her%20case.%20She%20was%20told%20that%20if%20she%20felt%20comfortable%2C%20she%20should%20try%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20person%20who%20sent%20her%20the%20message.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20didn't%20want%20to%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20computer%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ms%20Jane%20replied%20to%20the%20message%2C%20the%20Instagram%20user%20who'd%20contacted%20her%20said%20he%20wanted%20more%20photos%20and%20%243%2C000.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20just%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20try%20and%20blackmail%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20upset.%20I'd%20never%20been%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this%20before%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5C