of%20his%20dad's%20eye%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-lincolnshire-68007571%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20visited%20their%20home%20on%20January%202%2C%20after%20contacting%20the%20father%20on%20December%2027.%20However%2C%20she%20received%20no%20reply%20and%2C%20after%20making%20inquiries%20at%20other%20addresses%20where%20the%20child%20might%20be%2C%20contacted%20the%20police.%20The%20social%20worker%20returned%20to%20the%20house%20unannounced%20two%20days%20later%20and%20contacted%20the%20cops%20again%20as%20there%20was%20still%20no%20response.%20The%20bodies%20of%20the%20father%20and%20the%20son%20were%20not%20found%20until%20the%20social%20worker%20got%20into%20the%20home%20using%20a%20key%20from%20the%20landlord%20days%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20Lincolnshire%20County%20Council's%20executive%20director%20of%20children's%20services%2C%20Heather%20Sandy%2C%20described%20the%20deaths%20as%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20tragedy%20that%20Kenneth%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%20He%20was%20at%20home%20on%20his%20own%20with%20Bronson%20and%20that%20meant%20that%20there%20was%20nobody%20left%20to%20give%20Bronson%20care%2C%20and%20sadly%20as%20a%20result%20of%20that%2C%20Bronson%20has%20also%20passed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnames-of-10-countries-with-highest-gold-reserves-revealed-know-indias-rank-4883838%5C%22%3ENames%20Of%2010%20Countries%20With%20Highest%20Gold%20Reserves%20Revealed%2C%20Know%20India's%20Rank%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2F2024%2Fjan%2F17%2Fbronson-battersby-two-year-old-boy-died-of-starvation-curled-up-next-to-dead-father%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20boy's%20mother%20Sarah%20Piesse%20said%20she%20last%20saw%20her%20son%20before%20Christmas%20after%20a%20row%20with%20Mr%20Kenneth.%20The%2060-year-old%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20no%20earlier%20than%2029%20December.%20The%202-year-old%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20died%20of%20dehydration%20and%20starvation%2C%20according%20to%20a%20postmortem%20report%20seen%20by%20the%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELincolnshire%20Police%20has%20said%20it%20was%20not%20treating%20the%20deaths%20as%20suspicious%20but%20had%20referred%20itself%20to%20the%20Independent%20Office%20for%20Police%20Conduct%20(IOPC)%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20standard%20procedure%20in%20such%20cases.%20Lincolnshire%20County%20Council%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20rapid%20review%20into%20the%20incident.%20The%20rapid%20review%20will%20involve%20the%20council%2C%20police%20force%2C%20and%20any%20relevant%20health%20organisations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705561560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fuk-police_625x300_1530874537613.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-2-died-of-starvation-found-curled-up-next-to-dead-father-4884920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%202-year-old%20boy%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20was%20found%20starved%20to%20death%20next%20to%20the%20body%20of%20his%20father%2C%20who%20had%20suffered%20a%20fatal%20heart%20attack%20two%20weeks%20earlier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-2-died-of-starvation-found-curled-up-next-to-dead-father-4884920%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-2-died-of-starvation-found-curled-up-next-to-dead-father-4884920%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-2-died-of-starvation-found-curled-up-next-to-dead-father-4884920%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Refuses%20to%20Cancel%20Rally%20of%20BJP%20Leader%20Infamous%20for%20Hate%20Speech%2C%20Stoking%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F25115737%2F22.2.22-58.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20issued%20directives%20to%20district%20magistrates%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Yavatmal%20and%20Chhattisgrah%E2%80%99s%20Raipur%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Etake%20appropriate%20measures%20in%20response%20to%20concerns%20about%20potential%20hate%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20upcoming%20rallies%20organised%20by%20the%20Hindu%20Janajagruti%20Samiti%20(HJS)%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20legislator%20T.%20Raja%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHJS%20plans%20to%20conduct%20rallies%20in%20Yavatmal%20on%20January%2018%20and%20in%20Raipur%20from%20January%2019%20to%20January%2025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20halt%20the%20rallies%2C%20it%20instructed%20the%20district%20magistrates%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20hate%20speech%20occurs%20during%20these%20events.%20The%20court%20also%20suggested%20the%20installation%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20the%20locations%20to%20identify%20perpetrators%20in%20case%20of%20any%20%E2%80%9Cuntoward%20incidents%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20came%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20an%20interlocutory%20application%20seeking%20to%20deny%20permission%20for%20the%20rallies.%20The%20application%20included%20transcripts%20of%20alleged%20hate%20speeches%20made%20by%20the%20organisations%20and%20Singh%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20representing%20applicant%20Shaheen%20Abdullah%2C%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20against%20Singh%20despite%20previous%20FIRs.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20event%20takes%20place%2C%20we%20come%20to%20this%20court%20and%20an%20FIR%20is%20lodged.%20But%20nothing%20is%20done.%20Then%20he%20continues%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20speeches.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20all%20this%20then%3F%20See%20the%20kind%20of%20hatred%20he%20is%20propagating!%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Justice%20Khanna%20acknowledged%20the%20objectionable%20nature%20of%20the%20speeches%2C%20he%20stressed%20upon%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20intervene%20once%20the%20criminal%20justice%20process%20is%20set%20in%20motion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20through%20%5Bthe%20speeches%5D.%20Certainly%20objectionable.%20%5BBut%5D%20this%20court%20has%20already%20issued%20directions%2C%20including%20regarding%20CCTV%20cameras.%20As%20far%20as%20processions%20are%20concerned%E2%80%A6we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20that.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20any%20hate%20speech%20or%20incitement%20to%20violence%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%20But%20we%20cannot%20preempt%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Datta%20pointed%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20perpetrators%20should%20be%20parties%20in%20the%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20he%20a%20party%3F%20Your%20request%2C%20if%20granted%2C%20will%20affect%20someone.%20Your%20prayer%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20permission%20is%20not%20granted%20to%20X%20or%20withdraw%20permission%20if%20already%20granted%3F%20How%20can%20we%20pass%20this%20order%20without%20this%20person%20being%20a%20party%20or%20hearing%20them%3F%20This%20goes%20against%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20happen%20again%20and%20again%20unless%20your%20lordships%20intervene%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20said%20at%20the%20end.%20However%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20passed%20orders.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20we%20had%20passed%20orders%20and%20it%20did%20stop.%20That%20is%20the%20positive%20part.%20Why%20only%20look%20at%20the%20negative%20aspect%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20booked%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Police%20on%20January%207%20for%20allegedly%20making%20incendiary%20speeches%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Solapur%20on%20January%206.%20During%20the%20rally%2C%20he%20allegedly%20urged%20his%20audience%20to%20assault%20%E2%80%9Clove%20jihadis%E2%80%9D%20and%20boycott%20products%20with%20halal%20certification%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENews%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Ftelangana-bjp-mla-raja-singh-booked-for-hate-speech-in-maharashtras-solapur-rally%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20term%20Hindutva%20politicians%20have%20coined%20and%20used%20to%20describe%20an%20imaginary%20conspiracy%20in%20which%20Muslim%20men%20supposedly%20dupe%20