A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong-asia-film-financing-forum-haf-wang-xiaoshuai-josh-kim-fukada-koji-1235876019%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muslim%20Teen%20Lost%20Home%20For%20'Spitting'%20On%20Hindu%20Rally%2C%20Now%20Witness'%20Flip-Flop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdnan%20Mansuri%2C%2018%2C%20spent%20151%20days%20in%20judicial%20custody%20for%20allegedly%20spitting%20on%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20procession%20in%20his%20hometown%20Ujjain.%20His%20home%20was%20demolished%20soon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20citing%20encroachment%2C%20and%20the%20family%20had%20to%20find%20another%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20after%20five%20months%20behind%20bars%2C%20the%20teenager%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20because%20the%20complainant%2C%20also%20the%20prime%20witness%2C%20refused%20to%20identify%20him.%20His%20minor%20brother%20and%20his%20cousin%2C%20also%20a%20minor%2C%20are%20the%20two%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20They%20were%20granted%20bail%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%20Adnan%20and%20his%20two%20brothers%20were%20on%20the%20terrace%20when%20a%20procession%20of%20Lord%20Mahakal%20-%20another%20name%20for%20Lord%20Shiva%20-%20taken%20out%20by%20devotees%20passed%20by%20their%20house.%20Someone%20shouted%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20spit%2C%20they%20spit%26quot%3B.%20That%20was%20it.%20The%20three%20boys%20were%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20their%20home%20was%20demolished.%20The%20local%20administration%20cited%20encroachment.%20As%20the%20bulldozer%20went%20to%20work%2C%20a%20DJ%20system%20was%20called%20in.%20Loudspeakers%20blared%20and%20dhols%20were%20beaten%20as%20Adnan's%20family%20lost%20their%20home.%20Ashish%20Agarwal%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20then%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20insult%20Lord%20Shiva%20will%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20Shiv%20Tandav%20too%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdnan%20and%20his%20brothers%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20were%20charged%20with%20outraging%20religious%20feelings%2C%20promoting%20enmity%2C%20disturbing%20religious%20assembly%20and%20public%20mischief.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Ujjain%20resident%20Sawan%20Lot.%20While%20his%20minor%20brothers%20were%20granted%20bail%2C%20he%20remained%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Monday%2C%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20in%20Indore%20granted%20bail%20to%20Adnan.%20In%20its%20two-page%20order%2C%20the%20judge%20noted%20that%20complainant%20Sawan%20Lot%2C%20also%20the%20prosecution's%20witness%20number%201%2C%20and%20Ajay%20Khatra%2C%20witness%20number%202%2C%20turned%20hostile%20before%20the%20trial%20court%20and%20did%20not%20support%20the%20prosecution's%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Sawan%20Lot%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20Adnan.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20the%20boy%20whose%20video%20was%20shown%20to%20me%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20him.%20A%20direct%20video%20call%20was%20made%20from%20the%20jail%20to%20the%20court.%20I%20refused%20to%20identify%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Lot%20said%2C%20he%20had%20seen%20the%20other%20two%20boys%20at%20the%20spot%20of%20the%20incident%20on%20July%2017%20and%20had%20identified%20them.%20The%20complainant%20added%20that%20demolishing%20Adnan's%20house%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20needed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevendra%20Singh%20Sengar%2C%20counsel%20for%20the%20accused%2C%20said%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20case%20show%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20not%20investigated%20properly.%20%26quot%3BThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20complainant%20didn't%20support%20the%20prosecution's%20theory%20that%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR.%20He%20refused%20to%20identify%20the%20accused%20and%20also%20said%20he%20had%20not%20seen%20the%20incident%20taking%20place.%20The%20prosecution's%20other%20witness%2C%20Ajay%20Khatri%2C%20also%20turned%20hostile%20and%20didn't%20identify%20Adnan%20as%20the%20one%20who%20committed%20the%20alleged%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20exposes%20that%20in%20such%20a%20religiously%20sensitive%20case%2C%20the%20police%20haven't%20investigated%20the%20matter%20carefully%20and%20seriously.%20Even%20the%20house%20of%20the%20family%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20family%20was%20harassed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdnan's%20father%20Ashraf%20has%20lost%20his%20home%20but%20his%20happy%20that%20his%20son%20is%20back.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20anything%20from%20anyone%2C%20the%20children%20have%20been%20granted%20bail.%20Now%20I%20just%20want%20them%20to%20be%20acquitted%2C%20that's%20all%20I%20want.%20I%20don't%20care%20about%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20demolition%20of%20his%20house%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20anti-encroachment%20campaign%20is%20about%20to%20begin%20so%20the%20house%20would%20have%20been%20demolished%20anyway.%20I%20have%20to%20run%20a%20shop%20there.%20Everyone%20knows%20something%20wrong%20has%20happened.%20We%20just%20want%20the%20children%20to%20be%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Kharakuwa%20police%20station%2C%20where%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%2C%20cops%20are%20tight-lipped.%20Asked%20about%20the%20case%2C%20police%20officer%20Livan%20Kujur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20has%20been%20completed%20and%20the%20charge%20sheet%20filed%20in%20the%20court.%20The%20matter%20is%20sub-judice%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20say%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705561140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjh82n98o_ujjain-house_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmuslim-teen-lost-home-for-spitting-on-hindu-rally-now-witness-flip-flop-4884880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adnan%20Mans