r%20take-off.%3Cp%3EMandai%20Wildlife%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Le%20didn't%20travel%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20accompanied%20by%20a%20keeper%20and%20veterinarian%20from%20Singapore%20and%20a%20zookeeper%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20giant%20panda%20cub%20was%20also%20served%20a%20special%20in-flight%20meal%20during%20his%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20bamboo%2C%20bamboo%20shoots%2C%20fruit%2C%20pellets%2C%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESIA%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Le%20Le%20arrived%20safely%20in%20China%20on%20January%2016.%20The%20panda%20cub%20is%20now%20being%20quarantined%2C%20and%20the%20China%20Conservation%20and%20Research%20Center%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3EGiant%20Panda%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewill%20soon%20assign%20Le%20Le%20to%20a%20new%2C%20permanent%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiant-panda-cub-travels-to-china-via-singapore-airlines-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705551544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a88d0f43bb77284b9dfced%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiant-panda-cub-travels-to-china-via-singapore-airlines-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore's%20first%20giant%20panda%20cub%2C%20Le%20Le%2C%20took%20a%204.5-hour-long%20flight%20to%20China%20via%20Singapore%20Airlines%20on%2016%20January%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiant-panda-cub-travels-to-china-via-singapore-airlines-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20rebranding%20plans%20for%20Ching's%20Secret%2C%20Smith%20%26amp%3B%20Jones%2C%20Organic%20India%3A%20Tata%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%