d%20Trump%20lawyer%20Alina%20Habba%20at%20least%2014%20times%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BSit%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20her%20at%20one%20point.%20When%20she%20asked%20for%20a%20sidebar%2C%20he%20tersely%20responded%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BNo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20did%20not%20seem%20at%20all%20happy%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tight-leash-e-jean-carroll-trial-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20during%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll's%20second%20sex%20assault%20defamation%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20often%20crossing%20his%20arms%2C%20glowering%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-heckling-e-jean-carroll-defamation-trial-judge-warning-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20muttering%20complaints%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20his%20seat%20at%20the%20defense%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20lead%20lawyer%20Alina%20Habba%20may%20have%20had%20an%20even%20worse%20time%20in%20that%20Manhattan%20courtroom%2C%20where%20Carroll%20hopes%20that%20a%20federal%20jury%20will%20hit%20Trump%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarroll-lawyer-urges-massive-damages-trump-defamation-trial-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonetary%20damages%20high%20enough%20to%20finally%20%26quot%3Bmake%20him%20stop%26quot%3B%20defaming%20her.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20day%2C%20and%20with%20Carroll%20herself%20on%20the%20stand%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Lewis%20Kaplan%20rebuked%20Habba%20from%20the%20bench%2C%20often%20schooling%20her%20in%20basic%20law%20in%20mini-lectures%20that%20showed%20mounting%20impatience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20judge%20tersely%20interrupted%20the%20lawyer%2C%20telling%20her%2C%20%26quot%3Bsit%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20in%20chronological%20order%2C%20are%20fourteen%20times%20Habba%20was%20taken%20to%20task%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20the%20fed-up%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20%26quot%3BI%20make%20the%20rulings%20here%2C%20not%20the%20lawyers%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20I%20heard%2C%20Ms.%20Habba%2C%20I%20do%20not%20need%20announcements%20from%20counsel%20on%20what%20they%20intend%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20instructed%2C%20when%20Habba%20interrupted%20Carroll's%20direct%20testimony%20by%20standing%20up%20and%20claiming%20that%20her%20opponents%20%26quot%3Bopened%20the%20door%26quot%3B%20on%20an%20issue%20that%20she%20would%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20address%20during%20cross-examination%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20make%20the%20rulings%20here%2C%20not%20the%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20added.%20When%20Habba%20tried%20to%20press%20her%20point%2C%20Kaplan%20told%20her%2C%20succinctly%2C%20%26quot%3BSit%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOK%2C%26quot%3B%20Habba%20said%2C%20sitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20do%20it%20my%20way%20in%20this%20courtroom%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHabba%20began%20an%20afternoon%20of%20cross-examination%20by%20suddenly%20confronting%20Carroll%20with%20her%20October%2C%202022%2C%20pre-trial%20deposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20a%20transcript%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20with%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20told%20Habba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20honor%2C%20it's%20on%20the%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Habba%20told%20the%20judge%2C%20who%2C%20for%20a%20second%20time%2C%20asked%20for%20a%20hard-copy%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20look%2C%20Ms.%20Habba%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20as%20her%20staff%20continued%20scrambling%20to%20get%20him%20a%20hard%20copy.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20do%20it%20my%20way%20in%20this%20courtroom%2C%20and%20that's%20all%20there%20is%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20you%20give%20me%20the%20page%20and%20line%20number%20you%20want%20me%20to%20focus%20on%2C%20without%20reading%20it%2C%20and%20then%20I'll%20l