0the%20ruler%20of%20the%20Valbaran%20fae%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Ruhn%20Danaan%2C%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20the%20Valbaran%20fae%2C%20is%20Bryce's%20half-brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20and%20Ruhn%20are%20heirs%20to%20the%20Starborn%20fae%20lineage%2C%20giving%20them%20power%20over%20starlight%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20wield%20the%20Starsword%2C%20an%20ancient%20sword%20forged%20from%20an%20actual%20star.%20Bryce%20has%20more%20starlight%20power%20than%20Ruhn%2C%20though%20he%20is%20a%20full-blooded%20fae.%20Ruhn%20also%20has%20power%20from%20his%20mother's%20lineage%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20wield%20shadows%20and%20speak%20into%20other%20people's%20minds%20%E2%80%94%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20he%20keeps%20secret%20from%20most%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20can%20blind%20people%20with%20her%20power%20and%20has%20an%20eight-pointed%20star%20scar%20on%20her%20chest%20that%20glows%20at%20different%20times.%20Bryce's%20power%20also%20allows%20her%20to%20teleport%2C%20and%20she%20can%20absorb%20other%20Vanir's%20powers%20for%20short%20bursts%20of%20time%20because%20she%20made%20the%20Drop%20through%20a%20gate%2C%20where%20Vanir%20drop%20their%20power%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6504a1c04afd900019c0081f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20her%20Starborn%20abilities%2C%20Bryce%20became%20a%20portal%20after%20her%20friend%20Danika%20Fendyr%20(more%20on%20her%20in%20a%20bit)%20inked%20Luna's%20Horn%2C%20a%20magical%20object%20that%20creates%20portals%2C%20onto%20her%20back%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20travel%20between%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20meets%20her%20mate%20Or