tnering%20with%20a%20human%20named%20Sofie%20Renast%20to%20uncover%20how%20the%20Asteri%20came%20to%20Midgard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a84f32dcdb354a98586b6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223039%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20her%20death%2C%20she%20also%20secretly%20mated%20the%20angel%20Baxian%20Argos%2C%20known%20to%20most%20as%20the%20Helhound%2C%20and%20left%20a%20luxury%20apartment%20to%20Bryce%20in%20her%20will%2C%20where%20she%20kept%20clues%20about%20her%20rebellious%20activities.%20Baxian%20tried%20to%20help%20Bryce%20and%20Hunt%20throughout%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Asteri%20took%20him%20prisoner%20alongside%20Ruhn%20and%20Hunt%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanika's%20pack%20included%20Connor%20Holstrom%2C%20her%20Second%2C%20who%20was%20romantically%20interested%20in%20Bryce.%20The%20Archangel%20Micah%20murdered%20Danika%2C%20Connor%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20pack%20after%20she%20stole%20Luna's%20Horn.%20Bryce%20killed%20Micah%20when%20she%20discovered%20who%20murdered%20her%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBryce%20and%20Ruhn's%20friends%20back%20them%20up%20throughout%20the%20series%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERuhn's%20best%20friends%20are%20Declan%20Emmet%20and%20Tristan%20Flynn%2C%20two%20fae%20with%20whom%20he%20went%20through%20his%20Ordeal%2C%20a%20magical%20challenge%20fae%20must%20overcome.%20The%20trio%20also%20work%20for%20the%20Auxiliary%2C%20Crescent%20City's%20law%20enforcement%20agency%2C%20and%20live%20in%20a%20house%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeclan%20is%20skilled%20at%20cyber%20security%2C%20often%20hacking%20into%20different%20networks