ith%20Bryce%20and%20Hunt%20to%20discover%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20Sofie%20Renast's%20brother%20Emile%2C%20though%20he%20backs%20off%20when%20he%20finds%20out%20Emile%20lacks%20magical%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETharion%20also%20leaves%20the%20River%20Queen's%20court%20in%20%26quot%3BHOSAB%2C%26quot%3B%20offering%20himself%20to%20the%20Viper%20Queen%20instead%20so%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20live%20underwater.%20A%20snake%20shifter%2C%20the%20Viper%20Queen%20rules%20over%20the%20Meat%20Market%20in%20Crescent%20City%2C%20where%20seedy%20dealings%20often%20go%20down.%20Those%20working%20for%20her%20often%20become%20addicted%20to%20her%20venom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIthan%20is%20Connor's%20younger%20brother%2C%20and%20he%20had%20a%20promising%20career%20as%20a%20sunball%20player%2C%20though%20he%20quit%20after%20his%20brother's%20death.%20Sabine%20Fendyr%2C%20Danika's%20mother%2C%20kicks%20him%20out%20of%20his%20wolf%20pack%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%26quot%3B%20for%20defending%20Bryce%20in%20the%20press%2C%20making%20him%20a%20lone%20wolf.%20Danika's%20father%20is%20Mordoc%2C%20a%20cruel%20dreadwolf%20who%20works%20for%20the%20Asteri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIthan%20also%20loved%20Bryce%2C%20which%20he%20always%20kept%20to%20himself%20because%20of%20Connor%20and%20Bryce's%20connection.%20In%20%26quot%3BHOSAB%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20goes%20with%20Bryce%20to%20a%20mystic%2C%20discovering%20a%20wolf%20shifter%20separated%20from%20her%20family.%20The%20Prime%20of%20the%20wolves%20reveals%20to%20him%20the%20wolf%20is%20likely%20the%20lost%20Fendyr%20heir%20who%20could%20challenge%20Sabine%20for%20the%20Prime%20position%20when%20he%20dies.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book%2C%20Ithan%20steals%20the%20unnamed%20wolf%20from%20the%20mystic%2C%20hoping%20to%20protect%20her%20from%20Sabine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20estranged%20half-sisters%20the%20Hind%2C%20aka%20Lidia%20Cervos%2C%20and%20Hypaxia%20Enador%20were%20major%20players%20in%20'HOSAB'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652420506561dd877e74aa04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHypaxia%20Enador%20became%20Queen%20of%20the%20Valbaran%20Witches%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%26quot%3B%20after%20her%20mother%20died.%20She%20is%20both%20a%20witch%20and%20a%20necromancer%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20dead.%20She%20inherited%20her%20necromancy%20gifts%20from%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20became%20queen%2C%20the%20Autumn%20King%20arranged%20a%20marriage%20between%20Ruhn%20and%20Hypaxia%2C%20hoping%20to%20increase%20the%20fae's%20power%20in%20Valbara.%20Ruhn%20and%20Hypaxia%20have%20friendly%20interactions%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20unbeknownst%20to%20him%2C%20the%20witch%20has%20a%20secret%20lover.%20She%20is%20involved%20with%20Celestina%2C%20the%20archangel%20who%20replaces%20Micah%20as%20Crescent%20City's%20governor%20after%20his%20death.%20Their%20relationship%20is%20a%20secret%20to%20all%20but%20Bryce%20and%20Hunt%2C%20who%20walk%20in%20on%20them%20being%20intimate%20at%20a%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELidia%20Cervos%20and%20Hypaxia%20share%20a%20mother%2C%20but%20Lidia's%20father's%20family%20raised%20her%20because%20she%20inherited%20his%20deer%20shifter%20gifts%20instead%20of%20her%20mother's%20witch%20powers.%20Lidia%20was%20recruited%20by%20the%20evil%20archangel%20Sandriel%20(who%20is%20killed%20by%20Hunt%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%26quot%3B)%20to%20join%20her%20triarii%2C%20and%20she%20became%20not%20only%20her%20spymaster%20but%20spymaster%20for%20the%20Asteri.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20cruel%20angel%20Pollux%20Antonius'%20lover%2C%20seeming%20to%20thrive%20among%20the%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unbeknownst%20to%20everyone%2C%20Lidia%20is%20a%20spy%20for%20the%20rebel%20group%20Ophion%2C%20going%20undercover%20as%20Agent%20Daybright%20with%20no%20one%20knowing%20she%20hates%20the%20Asteri%20and%20Pollux.%20Ruhn%2C%20as%20Agent%20Night%2C%20connects%20with%20Day%20using%20his%20mind-speaking%20powers%20while%20helping%20Bryce%20search%20for%20Emile%2C%20and%20they%20fall%20in%20love%20without%20knowing%20who%20the%20other%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELidia%20won't%20tell%20Ruhn%20who%20she%20is%20even%20after%20discovering%20his%20identity%2C%20only%20revealing%20herself%20to%20save%20him%20and%20Bryce%20when%20they%20are%20captured%20after%20breaking%20into%20the%20Asteri's%20Archives%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAidas%2C%20a%20Hel%20prince%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20free%20Midgard%20of%20the%20Asteri%2C%20which%20includes%20Rigelus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BCrescent%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryce%20has%20contact%20with%20Aidas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20princes%20of%20Hel.%20Rather%20than%20being%20a%20place%20of%20punishment%20for%20the%20dead%2C%20Hel%20is%20another%20planet%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BCrescent%20City%26quot%3B%20universe.%20It's%20considered%20an%20evil%20place%20to%20the%20public%2C%20particularly%20because%20demons%20can%20be%20called%20to%20Midgard%20from%20it.%20But%20Bryce%20discovered%20in%20%26quot%3BHOSAB%26quot%3B%20that%20Hel%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20help%20Midgard's%20citizens%20fight%20against%20the%20Asteri%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20The%20Asteri%20tried%20to%20conquer%20Hel%20before%20coming%20to%20Midgard%2C%20and%20the%20princes%20killed%20Sirius%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Asteri%2C%20while%20pushing%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAidas%20visited%20Bryce%20when%20she%20was%20a%20child%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20cat%2C%20and%20he%20later%20appeared%20to%20her%20as