%5C%22%3EPakistan%20recalled%20its%20ambassador%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Tehran%20and%20informed%20the%20Iranian%20envoy%2C%20who%20was%20not%20in%20the%20country%2C%20that%20he%20should%20not%20return%20to%20his%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20late-night%20reaction%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20it%20was%20understandable%20if%20a%20country%20took%20measures%20to%20defend%20its%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20matter%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%20Insofar%20as%20India%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20an%20uncompromising%20position%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20towards%20terrorism.%20We%20understand%20actions%20that%20countries%20take%20in%20their%20self-defence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20backing%20of%20the%20Iranian%20action%20was%20expected%2C%20given%20that%20New%20Delhi%20had%20publicly%20undertaken%20cross-border%20operations%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20purportedly%20targeting%20terrorist%20camps%2C%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20instance%20involved%20missile%20strikes%20in%202016%2C%20and%20the%20second%20included%20airstrikes%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20latter%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20retaliated%20by%20conducting%20air%20raids%20on%20military%20installations%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%20claimed%20that%20the%20target%20of%20this%20week%E2%80%99s%20missile%20strike%20was%20the%20Jaish%20al-Adl%20terror%20group%20that%20had%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20shelter%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balochistan%20province%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaish%20al-Adl%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Jundallah%2C%20had%20also%20been%20designated%20as%20a%20terror%20group%20by%20the%20US%20state%20department%20in%202010.%20It%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dni.gov%2Fnctc%2Fftos%2Fjaa_fto.html%5C%22%3Emost%20active%20and%20influential%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20Sunni%20militant%20group%20operating%20in%20the%20Iran-Pakistan%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Amir-Abdollahian%20said%20that%20Iran%20respected%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Pakistan%20but%20would%20not%20%E2%80%9Callow%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%5BIran%E2%80%99s%5D%20national%20security%20to%20be%20compromised%20or%20played%20with%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnone%20of%20the%20nationals%20of%20the%20friendly%20and%20brotherly%20country%20of%20Pakistan%20were%20targeted%20by%20Iranian%20missiles%20and%20drones%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Iranian%20officials%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-iran-pakistan-idUSKCN1Q507R%5C%22%3Eoften%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0threatened%20to%20conduct%20military%20raids%20into%20Pakistan%20after%20any%20major%20action%20by%20Jaish%20al-Adl.%20In%202014%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20to%20make%20it%20publicly%20clear%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1090985%5C%22%3EIranian%20security%20forces%20were%20not%20allowed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20conduct%20operations%20inside%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Iran%20may%20have%20sent%20missiles%20into%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20Iranian%20security%20forces%20may%20have%20intruded%20beyond%20the%20border%20once%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Fasia-pacific%2Firan-frees-2-soldiers-kidnapped-in-pakistan%2F2132654%5C%22%3EIran%E2%80%99s%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20had%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20it%20freed%20two%20border%20guards%20who%20were%20taken%20as%20hostages%20by%20Jaish%20al-Adl%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuccessful%20operation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20had%20not%20only%20condemned%20the%20action%20and%20recalled%20its%20envoy%2C%20but%20also%20stopped%20all%20scheduled%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretaker%20Pakistan%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Jalil%20Abbas%20Jilani%2C%20told%20his%20counterpart%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20today%20that%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20missile%20attack%20had%20caused%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20damage%E2%80%9D%20to%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20foreign%20minister%20added%20that%20Pakistan%20reserved%20the%20right%20to%20respond%20to%20this%20provocative%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20foreign%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%20%3C%2Fem%3Enewspaper%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20delegation%20left%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20joint%20border%20trade%20committee%20in%20the%20Iranian%20port%20of%20Chabahar%20midway%20on%20Wednesday.%20It%20also%20decided%20to%20postpone%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Chabahar%20Free%20Zone%20Business%20Exhibition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20on%20Iranian%20security%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20clashes%20with%20an%20armed%20group%20in%20the%20Iranian%20province%20of%20Sistan-Baluchestan%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20five%20Iranian%20border%20guards.%20State%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20attributed%20to%20%E2%80%98infiltrators%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20in%20separate%20incidents%2C%20at%20least%20six%20Iranian%20policemen%20lost%20their%20lives.%20In%20the%20latest%20attack%20last%20month%2C%2011%20police%20officers%20died%20following%20an%20assault%20on%20a%20police%20station%20in%20the%20Iranian%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20inside%20Pakistan%20occurred%20one%20day%20after%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20launched%20ballistic%20missiles%20against%20%E2%80%9Celements%20and%20agents%20of%20Mossad%E2%80%9D%20in%20Iraq%E2%80%99s%20semi-autonomous%20Kurdistan%20region%20and%20at%20%E2%80%9Canti-Iran%20terror%20groups%E2%80%9D%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIraq%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmofa.gov.iq%2F2024%2F41999%2F%5C%22%3Erecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20ambassador%20to%20Iran%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmofa.gov.iq%2F2024%2F42016%2F%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20complaining%20against%20Iran%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20violation%20on%20Iraq%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%2C%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20and%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Iraqi%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20France%20have%20condemned%20the%20Iranian%20attack%20in%20Iraq%2C%20but%20have%20yet%20to%20react%20to%20the%20missile%20strikes%20inside%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705517203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18000710%2FMissile.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-seemingly-justifies-iran-missile-attack-in-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20backing%20of%20the%20Iranian%20action%20was%20expected%2C%20given%20that%20New%20Delhi%20had%20publicly%20undertaken%20cross-border%20operations%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20purportedly%20targeting%20terrorist%20camps%2C%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-seemingly-justifies-iran-missile-attack-in-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italian%20influencers%20to%20be%20bound%20by%20tighter%20rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705516849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F15E4A%2Fproduction%2