3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20313px)%2085vw%2C%20313px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17170654%2F71B3tndPxIL._SL1500_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22313%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17170654%2F71B3tndPxIL._SL1500_.jpg%20782w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17170654%2F71B3tndPxIL._SL1500_-196x300.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17170654%2F71B3tndPxIL._SL1500_-667x1024.jpg%20667w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693365%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22481%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPradeep%20K%20Saha%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Learning%20Trap%20%E2%80%93%20How%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20Took%20Indian%20Edtech%20for%20a%20Ride%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Publisher%3A%20Juggernaut%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaha%20charts%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20charismatic%20teacher%20to%20a%20status%20where%20he%20(and%20his%20family%2C%20who%20held%20controlling%20roles%20in%20the%20company)%20were%20clearly%20out%20of%20their%20depth%2C%20especially%20in%20financial%20matters.%20By%20the%20end%2C%20there%20seems%20little%20doubt%20that%20there%20is%20rampant%20denial%20and%20fraud%2C%20alongside%20the%20financial%20heartbreak%20of%20so%20many%20families%20and%20young%20men%20and%20women.%20The%20scepticism%20of%20these%20families%20toward%20education%20technology%20will%20likely%20never%20be%20allayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaha%20quotes%20many%20heart-breaking%20stories%20of%20how%20low-income%20families%20(such%20as%20even%20auto%20rickshaw%20drivers)%20were%20exploited%20%E2%80%93%20some%20were%20denied%20refunds%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20online%20subscriptions%20caused%20many%20families%20to%20bleed%20money%2C%20and%20end%20up%20in%20debt%20traps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%2C%20what%20is%20most%20useful%20about%20Saha%E2%80%99s%20book%20is%20that%20it%20speaks%20to%20the%20larger%20educational%20milieu%20of%20India.%20As%20written%2C%20most%20media%20hardly%20investigate%20education.%20This%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20larger%20fawning%20business%20media%20landscape%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prowess.%20Misunderstandings%20regarding%20education%20are%20rather%20more%20significant%20than%20fraudulent%20practices%20in%20say%2C%20a%20food-delivery%20app.%20The%20very%20idea%20that%20an%20education%20app%20can%20do%20so%20much%20%E2%80%93%20no%20less%20than%20transform%20your%20life%20%E2%80%93%20is%20itself%20unquestioned%20in%20our%20endless%20faith%20in%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20media%20does%20cover%20education%20it%20is%20mostly%20to%20bemoan%20the%20fact%20that%20Indian%20universities%20rarely%20feature%20in%20the%20list%20of%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20There%20is%20thus%20a%20stark%20contradiction%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20a%20certain%20segment%20may%20indeed%20bemoan%20this%20but%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20is%20simply%20taken%20for%20granted%2C%20as%20Saha%20writes%2C%20that%20the%20IIT-JEE%20or%20NEET%20or%20UPSC%20dream%20is%20only%20natural%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoor-working-conditions-abusive-practices-byjus-staff-reveal-harsh-work-conditions%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Treated%20Like%20Slaves%2C%20Abusive%20Practices%E2%80%99%3A%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20Staff%20Reveal%20Harsh%20Work%20Conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20chief%20reasons%20that%20Indian%20universities%20%E2%80%93%20even%20the%20lauded%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20do%20well%20in%20rankings%20is%20that%20the%20admission%20process%20is%20designed%20to%20exclude.%20Entrance%20exams%20are%20choke%20points%20%E2%80%93%20their%20design%20is%20fundamental.%20A%20truly%20good%20university%20would%20have%20a%20broad-based%20entrance%20process%20that%20looks%20at%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20a%20student%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20why%20top%20international%20universities%20insist%20on%20many%20dimensions.%20Not%20just%20test%20scores%2C%20but%20personal%20essays%2C%20fuller%20CVs%20of%20achievements%20and%20individual%20projects%2C%20interviews%2C%20etc.%20Indian%20universities%20are%20rarely%20willing%20to%20spend%20resources%20to%20hire%20trained%20admission%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20simply%20seen%20as%20an%20expense%20in%20both%20private%20and%20public%20sector%20universities.%20Most%20public%20universities%20would%20rather%20save%2C%20and%20most%20private%20universities%20would%20rather%20spend%20money%20on%20more%20direct%20marketing.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20choke%20point%20that%20the%20test%20prep%20industry%20thrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20trust%20in%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20top%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20and%20hence%20it%20is%20convenient%20for%20everyone%20to%20simply%20look%20at%20a%20number%20in%20a%20single%20test%20%E2%80%93%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cmerit%E2%80%9D.%20This%20deeply%20damaged%20ecosystem%20is%20where%20apps%20like%20Byjus%20(and%20many%20others)%20thrive.%20Indeed%2C%20there%20is%20little%20discussion%20on%20how%20to%20make%20the%20debilitated%20school%20system%20more%20robust%20so%20that%20these%20technologies%2Fcenters%20can%20at%20best%20provide%20a%20supplementary%20role%20%E2%80%93%20of%20making%20learning%20more%20engaging%20and%20deeper.%20Rather%2C%20the%20school%20system%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20its%20evaluation%20sub-system%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20held%20accountable%20at%20all%2C%20and%20the%20boards%20only%20ruthlessly%20homogenise%20in%20their%20evaluations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Byju%E2%80%99s%2C%20as%20Saha%20notes%2C%20had%20initially%20tried%20to%20make%20learning%20genuinely%20more%20engaging%20with%20animations%20and%20visualisations%2C%20and%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20believe%20that%20at%20one%20point%20Raveendran%20must%20have%20been%20a%20sincere%20teacher%20sharing%20his%20joy.%20The%20problem%20remains%20that%20if%20everything%20is%20anyway%20geared%20toward%20a%20few%20scores%20in%20a%20few%20exams%2C%20there%20is%20little%20learning%20%E2%80%93%20among%20other%20things%2C%20learning%20cannot%20happen%20in%20this%20atmosphere%20of%20high%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20is%20geared%20toward%20the%20test-giving%20authority%20being%20able%20to%20plausibly%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20not%20biased%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20many%20of%20the%20elements%20of%20these%20tests%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20learning%20(or%20creativity)%2C%20but%20entirely%20to%20do%20with%20irrelevant%20skills%20such%20as%20being%20able%20to%20do%20a%20problem%20with%20tricks%20that%20increase%20speed.%20It%20is%20in%20these%20hacks%20that%20these%20edtechs%20thrive%20%E2%80%93%20deeper%20learning%20is%20sacrificed.%20It%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20this%20learning%20at%20this%20crucial%20age%20that%20will%20then%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20these%20students%20to%20ever%20think%20creatively.%20Is%20it%20any%20wonder%20then%20that%20this%20pool%20of%20students%2C%20and%20the%20faculty%20that%20has%20to%20accommodate%20this%2C%20can%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20do%20serious%20Nobel%20Prize%20winning%20work%2C%20and%20have%20to%20go%20abroad%20if%20they%20have%20any%20such%20inclination.%20This%20indeed%20is%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20answer%20to%20why%20no%20Indian%20universities%20feature%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20rankings%20%E2%80%93%20college%20years%20are%20spent%20simply%20cleaning%20up%20the%20learning-loss%20of%20the%20admission%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20urgent%20than%20rankings%20is%20the%20thought%20that%20all%20our%20doctors%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20civil%20servants%20also%20come%20through%20such%20a%20compromised%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20grateful%20to%20Saha%20for%20these%20uncommon%20book-length%20explorations%20of%20the%20educational%20ecosystem%20and%20its%20sometimes%20bizarre%20manifestations%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20many%20more%20such%20extended%2C%20critical%20explorations.%C2%A0%20Recently%2C%20far%20more%20laudatory%20books%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20Nistha%20Tripathi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EUnstartup%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20while%20providing%20useful%20context%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%20simply%20reproduce%20the%20self-image%20of%20the%20founders%20and%20those%20who%20have%20a%20direct%20financial%20stake%20in%20these%20technologies.%20One%20is%20however%20glad%20for%20all%20these%20books%20%E2%80%93%20they%20teach%20us%20that%20there%20are%20no%20easy%20lessons%2C%20and%20that%20all%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%93%20students%2C%20parents%2C%20technologies%2C%20and%20universities%20%E2%80%93%20must%20all%20be%20thoughtfully%20invested%20in%20the%20task%20of%20rethinking%20education%20and%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENikhil%20Govind%20is%20a%20Professor%20and%20Head%20of%20the%20Manipal%20Centre%20for%20Humanities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705496045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17181640%2FEffect-69.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcharting-the-rise-and-fall-of-byjus-and-educational-ecosystem-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pradeep%20Saha's%20latest%20book%20'The%20Learning%20Trap%20%E2%80%93%20How%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20Took%20Indian%20Edtech%20for%20a%20Ride'%20is%20an%20uncommon%20investigative%20treatise%20into%20India's%20education%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcharting-the-rise-and-fall-of-byjus-and-educational-ecosystem-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20search%20Gibraltar%20car%20park%20for%20Royal%20Navy%20sailor%20missing%20since%201986%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170