%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20loan%2C%20Gaurav%20worked%20diligently%20to%20make%20his%20family%20business%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCall%20it%20fate%2C%20but%20the%20business%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20yielding%20much%20profit%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20pressure%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20began%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20more%20lucrative%20ventures.%20One%20thing%20I%20was%20clear%20about%20%E2%80%93%20I%20wanted%20to%20run%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20numerous%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20planters%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Solan%20who%20were%20earning%20substantial%20incomes.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20market%20saturated%20with%20producers%2C%20prices%20were%20steadily%20decreasing.%20I%20realised%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20something%20different.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20options%20online%20is%20when%20he%20found%20out%20about%20the%20precious%20%E2%80%98red%20gold%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20saffron.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20how%20expensive%20saffron%20is%20and%20how%20profitable%20it%20can%20be.%20However%2C%20I%20always%20assumed%20that%20it%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20started%20researching%20on%20the%20internet%20if%20there%20were%20ways%20of%20growing%20it%20in%20Himachal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20internet%20has%20all%20the%20answers%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20found%20out%20about%20the%20technique%20of%20using%20a%20controlled%20environment%20for%20growing%20different%20types%20of%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20a%20few%20instances%20where%20people%20grew%20saffron%20%3Ca%