%20commerce%20background%20and%20the%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20a%20test%20tube%20was%20during%20my%20training.%20Such%20small%20achievements%20motivate%20me%20to%20strive%20for%20the%20success%20of%20my%20company.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20now%20I%C2%A0do%20not%20keep%20a%20plan%20B%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanker%20has%20also%20been%20conferred%20with%20Progressive%20%26amp%3B%20Innovative%20Farmer%20awards%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20in%202019%20and%20Innovative%20Agricultural%20Startup%20by%20the%20Startup%20India%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmasshree%20Pande.%20All%20images%3A%20Shanker%20Meena.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705071179000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wondering%20how%20to%20start%20a%20mushroom%20business%3F%20Rajasthan's%20Shanker%20Meena%20founded%20'Jeevan%20Mushrooms'%2C%20a%20successful%20mushroom%20spawns'%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20his%20garage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20National%20Parks%20in%20India%20for%20The%20Perfect%20Wildlife%20Safari%20This%20Winter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESki%20destinations%2C%20snow-capped%20mountains%2C%20and%20beach%20resorts%20are%20typical%20choices%20for%20a%20winter%20break%20vacation.%20However%2C%20envision%20this%20alternative%20%E2%80%94%20encountering%20a%20majestic%20leopard%20sprawled%20across%20a%20moss-covered%20branch%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Periyar%20or%20tracking%20the%20elusive%20paw%20prints%20of%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276152%2Fkangsing-snow-ice-sculpture-associa